<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THLICHIA A HRANGMI IN CH211</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Totho thlichia hrangmi chung le, Ngaihchiat tilet a thomi in, Daihnak
 le dornak hmun a um, Velngeihnak thutdan toi ah khan.

[V2]
 Jesuh nih a thisen sungin, Kannih vialte a kan tlanh cang, Thisen
 cawkmi velngeih thutdan, Kan ca hnangamnak hmun a si.

[V3]
 Thlarau lung khat tlonlen tinak, Hawikom rualremnak hmun a um, Dang
 tlei hmanh zumh in an leng ti, Velngeihnak thutdan velchum ah.

[V4]
 Va bangin van ah kan zuang lai, Sual hnahnawh ti lo hmun ah khin;
 Pathian sunpar lianhngannak nih, Velngeih thutdan a khuh tikah.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<hymn_number>211</hymn_number>
</song>